Pre-Apocalypse[]: Nothing is known about Duke's life prior to or as the outbreak began.
Post-Apocalypse[]: At some point in the apocalypse, Duke somehow came into contact with a group named "the Saviors" which he subsequently joined. Duke aided his group in terrorizing other survivors and communities around the area into subjugating to Negan's will, where their victims would be forced to give half their supplies in exchange for not being murdered. Duke is among the Saviors to raid the Kingdom with Gavin . He stands guard around the captured townspeople as Gavin demands them to hand over King Ezekiel . Duke is carrying out orders until he is taken out by Morgan and Carol as they sneak around the Kingdom on a rescue mission. Gavin attempts to radio Duke for his location but is unsuccessful in receiving an answer, leading him to believe something wasn't right.
Death[]: Killed By Morgan Jones While guarding the Kingdom as Ezekiel is about to be taken to the Sanctuary, Duke has his throat slashed then stabbed in the chest and head by Morgan.
